<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>오렌지Pay 로그아웃 | 신용카드현금화 휴대폰소액결제</title>
    <meta name="description" content="오렌지Pay 로그아웃 페이지입니다.">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; }
        .bg-custom-orange { background-color: #FF7F50; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="max-w-md mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl p-8 text-center">
        <div class="mb-6">
            <div class="bg-green-100 rounded-full p-4 w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">로그아웃 완료</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-600">안전하게 로그아웃되었습니다.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
            <a href="index.html" 
               class="block w-full bg-custom-orange hover:bg-orange-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition">
                홈으로 돌아가기
            </a>
            
            <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">다시 상담이 필요하시면 언제든지 연락주세요!</p>
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                    <a href="https://pf.kakao.com/_SBFexb/chat" target="_blank" 
                       class="bg-yellow-400 hover:bg-yellow-500 text-gray-900 font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded transition">
                        카카오톡 문의
                    </a>
                    <a href="tel:010-5842-9536" 
                       class="text-custom-orange hover:text-orange-600 font-bold transition">
                        전화: 010-5842-9536
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                &copy; <span id="currentYear"></span> 오렌지Pay. All Rights Reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('currentYear').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
        
        // URL에서 back_url 파라미터 처리
        const urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
        const backUrl = urlParams.get('back_url');
        if (backUrl) {
            try {
                const decodedUrl = decodeURIComponent(backUrl);
                setTimeout(() => {
                    window.location.href = decodedUrl.startsWith('/') ? decodedUrl : '/';
                }, 3000);
            } catch (e) {
                console.log('Invalid back_url parameter');
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>